enhanced_by.method_name: predicatedSortedMap(SortedMap<K, V>, Predicate<? super K>, Predicate<? super V>)
enhanced_by.reason: Both methods involve creating a new PredicatedSortedMap instance with a SortedMap and predicates.
subMap relies on the state of the SortedMap obtained from getSortedMap() to create a new subMap.
headMap and subMap both involve creating a new SortedMap subset, and headMap might be invoked before subMap in certain test scenarios.
tailMap and subMap both involve creating a new SortedMap subset, and tailMap might be invoked before subMap in certain test scenarios.
